{"tid":928841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖奧：日本是最適合生活的國家 中國的廢氣和霧霾讓人難受！！","createTime":"2018-12-05T06:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T09:26:15.000Z","uid":10338,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d1dd46259051d23f491a7c197a3adbaeb92e2a","tid":928841,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"足球媒體&ldquo;GOAL&rdquo;報導，曾經在江蘇蘇寧效力、現效力於日本J聯賽名古屋鯨魚的巴西前鋒表示，日本是最適合生活的國家，中國的空氣污染讓他感到非常難受。<br />\n<br />\n本賽季，31歲的祖奧在J聯賽中出場了31次，打進了24球，獲得J聯賽金靴。若在採訪中表示：&ldquo;我認為日本是最適合生活的國家。在中國，廢氣和霧霾讓人感覺非常難受。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2016年若離開了阿聯酋聯賽加盟江蘇蘇寧，但是僅僅半個賽季之後他就離開了這支球隊。之後他回到了哥連泰斯，榮膺射手王和賽季MVP。"},{"pid":"ba760e6c83c12179623c11b93a93686da99d2a65","tid":928841,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"若"},{"pid":"c862f5b1ccc83b887b37923426fe3674b87b3a36","tid":928841,"uid":166785,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"搵夠走囉<br />\n九成九支那人都知支那唔好住"},{"pid":"0fca83f35410b4e89ac729cede087c5c889a9a94","tid":928841,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"捉佢去新疆再教育啦，咁多口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb52bd2612d13bc40ea1026337cb8baf4c4b997","tid":928841,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"死鏝狗"},{"pid":"d57b2c72b759521399c5bf9445cabfef74845bcc","tid":928841,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"唔係人工咁高囉wo"},{"pid":"bf52108e69e671b4728bad576e13789cb75f4c2f","tid":928841,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"支那卡高"}]}